snippet.title: CoH: Modern Combat - Trailer 5
snippet.description:
This is the 5th trailer for CoH: Modern Combat. With this one we want to especially showcase our updated engine, weapon and speech sounds, which have been adjusted to be accurate.
Further you can see the first moving pictures of our fully updated Humvee, Stryker and Bradley, as well as the vertical firing mode on the Javelin. We hope you like it.
Be sure to visit us on http://moderncombat.blacksandstudio.com
